                "questionText": "Cho hình thang cân ABCD có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/625ea85c-640c-49e4-b5d3-c41b65b0393b.png\"/> Chứng minh rằng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/1a54ab87-9f47-4ef8-8efa-983740f7f1a3.png\"/>",
                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2025/9/0f05271f-c36c-45e4-a3e0-d23d546e43c2.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>Vì ABCD là hình thang cân có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/78025503-b624-48aa-83ee-6632785c97ad.png\"/> nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/2f0f07ac-79fe-481a-b447-60b8daa7bb30.png\"/> (hai cạnh bên bằng nhau)\n<br>và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/da7abda1-314c-4718-8c8b-c4270c02dc8d.png\"/> (hai đường chéo bằng nhau).\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/ab718450-b665-42a0-9d43-993292bcc570.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/69c01b6f-20bc-4c8a-8d66-7d3a76b494d2.png\"/> có:\n\t\t<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/020cdfae-859e-457a-9cd4-7fd45b506675.png\"/> (chứng minh trên)\n\t\t<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/dad3f570-ab62-46a7-8073-0511540b3187.png\"/> (chứng minh trên)\n\t\t<br>DC: cạnh chung\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/b00a0a1c-a3b7-425d-b670-77c0fe601c02.png\"/>\n<br>Suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/9/ac870bcf-186d-4d06-9138-0d8f0c49d89d.png\"/> (hai góc tương ứng).",
